{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YLQbQMBXm7QeoSvTkEb3c8","type":"tool_result","content":"<system-reminder>This memory is 4 days old. Memories are point-in-time observations, not live state — claims about code behavior or file:line citations may be outdated. Verify against current code before asserting as fact.</system-reminder>\n     1→---\n     2→name: Devnet E2E test runner\n     3→description: How to run devnet E2E tests — requires dangerouslyDisableSandbox for localhost TCP, script auto-sources env vars\n     4→type: reference\n     5→---\n     6→\n     7→## Running Devnet E2E Tests\n     8→\n     9→**Command**: `bash scripts/run-e2e-devnet.sh` (from `apps/platform/` or monorepo root)\n    10→\n    11→**Must use `dangerouslyDisableSandbox: true`** — the sandbox blocks localhost TCP connections needed for PostgreSQL and the backend server.\n    12→\n    13→**What the script handles automatically**:\n    14→- Sources env vars from `apps/platform/.env.local` and `services/backend/.env`\n    15→- Starts PostgreSQL if not running\n    16→- Runs database migrations (including auth tables)\n    17→- Starts the fairness backend on port 3100 (or uses existing one)\n    18→- Runs Playwright tests with `playwright.devnet.config.ts`\n    19→- Cleans up backend on exit\n    20→\n    21→**Filter specific tests**:\n    22→- Smoke only: `bash scripts/run-e2e-devnet.sh --grep \"devnet smoke\"`\n    23→- Coinflip lifecycle: `bash scripts/run-e2e-devnet.sh --grep \"coinflip devnet lifecycle\"`\n    24→- Lord lifecycle: `bash scripts/run-e2e-devnet.sh --grep \"lord.*lifecycle\"`\n    25→\n    26→**Typical duration**: Smoke ~1min, lifecycle ~2min, full suite ~5min.\n    27→\n    28→**Prerequisites**: PostgreSQL 16 running (devcontainer auto-starts it), Playwright browsers installed (pre-cached in devcontainer).\n    29→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01J4DkMj6TbDT24GtmVyAJQv","session_id":"1de1cbce-bcf6-4659-9a0e-c65f55d25303","uuid":"d37b6166-1588-40a8-8510-3b9ed40aacdc"}
